{"tid":1788395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河南驚現習毛寺廟 「信徒」三拜九叩","createTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T18:03:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17c3daf94c6012de5f4c517c820557605accfa37","tid":1788395,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191218/K4B72DFPDTF6LPLPWAZYMN3SEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191218%2FK4B72DFPDTF6LPLPWAZYMN3SEU%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6l%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=71495d21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191218%2FK4B72DFPDTF6LPLPWAZYMN3SEU%2F&h=6f919ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191218/K4B72DFPDTF6LPLPWAZYMN3SEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n河南驚現習毛寺廟 「信徒」三拜九叩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地大舉查封佛寺道觀、拆毀佛像教堂十字架之際，河南省中部近期卻湧現一批供奉國家主席習近平及已故中共領導人毛澤東的廟宇。有佛教徒大表不滿，暗諷中共只准州官放火，不准百姓點燈：「要是沒有五星紅旗和毛澤東造像，寺廟就會被定為邪教！」<br />\n<br />\n該座供奉習近平及毛澤東的廟宇，名為「中原一點紅」，位於河南省汝州市。廟外亦有一尊毛澤東漢白玉石像，毛像前方桌上擺滿了供品，旁邊立着一座香爐。今年7月，有女民眾前來參拜，她向習近平和毛澤東畫像先三鞠躬，再三敬軍禮，然後跪地三拜九叩首，膜拜儀式怪異。當日，約有80多名民眾朝毛澤東像三拜九叩。據報，去年10月，該廟毛澤東像開光時，約有1,000多人前來參加。知情人士透露，該廟2017年建造至今已投資了十幾萬元人民幣，廟方還要繼續擴建。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576599623_3f59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576599623_3f59.jpg&h=7ffb5be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南民眾跪拜習近平與毛澤東畫像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佛教徒轟造神<br />\n<br />\n此外，河南省平頂山市郟縣一座佛教寺廟三皇姑寺六年前就供奉起毛澤東像，旁邊豎着國旗。許昌市一間商舖為保平安在店外貼上佛祖畫像，當地政府人員今年9月下旬以「佛祖像影響市容」為由，將其換為習的畫像。有郟縣佛教徒大表不滿，「毛澤東時代鏟除一切宗教信仰，卻天天讓人歌唱他是人民的大救星，背他的語錄。如今，習近平取締一切宗教信仰，他們都喊着沒神，自己卻成為人燒香跪拜的對象。」另一名佛教徒暗諷：「要是沒有五星紅旗和毛澤東造像，寺廟就會被定為邪教！」<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》網站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576599622_6135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576599622_6135.jpg&h=ac47dfd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寺廟外建有毛雕像。"},{"pid":"1b1cb4c54dbb966493fa8ec918b8fbd413f8fe5d","tid":1788395,"uid":86337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"弱撚智的中國人"},{"pid":"9d214a9e1660239ae27a2907d29e4410073f9fc9","tid":1788395,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>手足無證無據都生豬肉坐咗半年<br />\n又話手足唔係condom？<br />\n就快生豬肉到2020年<br />\n可唔可以幫手關注下呢單野<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGaZPt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGaZPt9.jpg&h=6915346d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7615a6b37f2133402714a5a82ab586e70fb723fb","tid":1788395,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f059c2347d781e7e11a363be701b53f24f4a7565","tid":1788395,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span st